title: Negans - Danse Macabre
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Danse Macabre is the debut EP release by Negans, a latest discovery by Neogoa Records. Full release is now available in WAV/FLAC and more via official Neogoa Records Bandcamp page - http://bit.ly/get-neg

01 - Midori (138 BPM)
02 - Into Asylum (140 BPM)
03 - Life On Earth (142 BPM)
04 - Danse Macabre (145 BPM)

All tracks written and produced by Negans (Elie Seigneur). For more Negans, please visit: 

Website: - http://www.neogoa.net/negans
Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/negans 
Twitter - http://www.twitter.com/negansmusic
SoundCloud - http://www.soundcloud.com/negans
